  "title": "fix(Pit): round the middle value to the whole number",
  "body": "Most prices start from > 0, which causes annoying decimal values at the middle.\r\n\r\nThis PR fixes that by always rounding the middle value to a whole number\r\n\r\nMaybe not a complete fix for #2275, but definitely related to the underlying reason.\r\n\r\nversion|result\r\n---|---\r\nbefore|<img width=\"1366\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-08-07 at 16 37 02\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6270048/29031533-dd964d6e-7b8e-11e7-8b8a-27d0239d70d9.png\">\r\nafter|<img width=\"1368\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-08-07 at 16 36 38\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6270048/29031538-e5692034-7b8e-11e7-9c01-aa22551b27ef.png\">\r\n\r\n",
